          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Assess Ruby Skills<br class="hidden sm:inline">
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">with Confidence</span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600 sm:text-xl leading-relaxed">
            Create timed exams from the official Ruby Silver question bank. Schedule rooms, invite candidates, and track results in real-time.
