            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">500+ curated questions covering all Ruby Silver certification topics: syntax, OOP, blocks, exceptions, and more.</p>
          </div>

          <%# Feature 2 %>
          <div class="group relative rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:ring-emerald-200">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 mb-6 transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:bg-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
